    <h3>Multi-Language Support</h3>
    <p>All course content is available in both Traditional Chinese (zh-TW) and English (en-US) via the <code>i18n</code> object. AI tools can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access Chinese content: <code>course.i18n["zh-TW"].title</code></li>
      <li>Access English content: <code>course.i18n["en-US"].title</code></li>
      <li>Use metadata for filtering: <code>course.metadata.grade_level</code>, <code>course.metadata.domain_category</code></li>
    </ul>
